{"tid":777570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"100公斤高三生被笑胖跳5樓亡　目擊同學「先笑後叫」55秒影片曝光","createTime":"2018-08-13T04:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T06:06:07.000Z","uid":34676,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"86a5edbc608121034cedadb2fe710c0bb462b224","tid":777570,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180812/1233356.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180812%2F1233356.htm&d=73UhWoOPSo7w239cqSuLYACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=95289822\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180812/1233356.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n反校園霸凌！泰國四色菊府（Sisaket）一名17歲高中生歐姆當著眾人面前，從學校的5樓跳下傷重不治，嚇得其他目擊學生放聲尖叫。據了解，死者體重100公斤，常因此被人嘲笑，可能因此想不開，如今55秒事發影片也曝光。悲劇發生後，平常欺負死者的學長紛紛致歉。<br />\n<br />\n▼歐姆身材較胖、體重100公斤，常因此被笑或捉弄而導致自卑。（圖／翻攝臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3479/3479272.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3479%2F3479272.jpg&h=aa80b970&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據學生拍攝的影片，歐姆（Oom）當時獨自翻過教學樓的5樓外牆，緩緩走在外側。當時在教學樓對面教室內的學生，一開始可能還以為歐姆在開玩笑，一群人還有說有笑，但看著他頭也不回地走到大樓邊緣，突然驚覺事態不對，許多人開始尖叫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3479/3479258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3479%2F3479258.jpg&h=15b68d3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3479/3479261.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3479%2F3479261.jpg&h=3374aad0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐姆站在5樓邊緣後，先慢慢往下看，他一度蹲低身體又站了起來，過了22秒後傳出一聲巨響，他墜落地面，全身骨頭碎裂傷重不治。許多目擊跳樓的學生也嚇得大叫。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，歐姆就讀高三，他身材較胖、體重100公斤，常被笑或捉弄而導致自卑，可能因此想不開輕生，詳細事發原因有待警方釐清。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">悲劇發生後，死者的同學都發文哀悼，還有一些平常欺負他的學長也表達歉意。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAP7HUAQyac\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfAP7HUAQyac&d=73UhWoOPSo7w239cqSuLYACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=52a3e0d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fAP7HUAQyac</a>"},{"pid":"0eba3c582ab8a4ab8050211c5c3447d9e8dc8829","tid":777570,"uid":135623,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"表達歉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7812881e3e6221f23f722ef07c7b4bec9d8f71d2","tid":777570,"uid":4203,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:36:36.000Z","msg":"翱翔於天際的夜鷹"},{"pid":"16b8b94fa89e69099cf47fff523347dfc8ca2b7c","tid":777570,"uid":54929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:36:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375bf60344685b75098a5834b6c0b64e30ddf2db","tid":777570,"uid":161731,"like":29,"dislike":7,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:37:38.000Z","msg":"真係變左死肥仔"},{"pid":"8640d64c7d6873d26d10368dedd719e4642a85cb","tid":777570,"uid":53421,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:37:43.000Z","msg":"比人笑樣衰都話&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n肥真係自己攞黎"},{"pid":"1aa9cfac1640544b6be13d53c57126f531a8cb7c","tid":777570,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:38:37.000Z","msg":"Oom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ec370e90b2fd56b2fa4b4b6b243ca6bb273e74","tid":777570,"uid":65406,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0eba3c582ab8a4ab8050211c5c3447d9e8dc8829","tid":777570,"uid":135623,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"表達歉意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T04:38:41.000Z"